s like that, he is temperate.\u201d It was said, \u201cWhat is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20829,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/08\/13\/dua-ease-answer-hardship\/","url_meta":{"origin":33755,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplicate in prosperity if you want answer in adversity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 13, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever would like for Allah to answer him during times of hardship and difficulty, let him supplicate often during times of ease.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3382 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24547,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/03\/22\/taqwa-love-people-as-yourself\/","url_meta":{"origin":33755,"position":4},"title":"Sufyan on Taqwa: Righteousness is to love people as yourself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Tha\u2019labi reported: Sufyan al-Thawri and Al-Fudayl, may Allah have mercy on them both, said, \u201cThe righteous man is he who loves for people what he loves for himself.\u201d And Al-Junayd ibn Muhammad, ma